title: P3D v2 ORBX libs 140201
description:
THIS INSTALLER IS A STAND-ALONE INSTALLER FOR P3D VERSION 2. There is a separate installer for FSX/P3Dv1.

 

This build of the Orbx Libraries replaces all previous versions.

 

** IMPORTANT!!  - INSTALL THIS LAST, AFTER ALL OTHER ORBX PATCHES ***

This installer will install Orbx Libraries V140201 to the FTXAA_ORBXLIBS directory in your ORBX Folder. It will update your Orbx Libraries to the latest version and is used by all Orbx products.

 

CHANGE LOG

-Changes to library objects to achieve compatibility with P3Dv2

-New autogen description files and models

-Change to installer behaviour
